    "Details": "The NNK-3 is an attempt to create a close quarters and urban warfare version. The variant mounts a vast array of anti-personal and vehicle weapons; ER Micro Lasers, AP Gauss Rifles and Heavy Machine Guns. For longer range engagements two Large Improved Heavy Lasers and two Large ER Pulse Lasers are kept. It is not recommended to fire both the long and short distance armaments simultaneously, as the cooling is very under-dimensioned.\n\n<b><color=#e62e00>Quirk: Improved Cooling Jacket - Laser</color></b>\n\n<b><color=#e62e00>Drop Cost Multiplier: 1.42</color></b>",
